rComments: Il s'attend à beaucoup trop. Ce cours semblait ne jamais finir et il n'est tellement PAS clair avec ses attentes.

QCM chaque semaine sur la matière qui n'a pas encore été vue. 6 livrables à faire + 2 rapports écrits, en plus de la simulation Intopia et toute la préparation pour celle-ci. Il corrige très sévèrement, selon s'il aime nos rapports ou non. Il donne une grille d'évalution, mais ne se fie pas sur celle-ci pour attribuer la note.

The worst class I have ever taken. The professor doesn't give any criteria grid. He will grade your work only on the fact that he likes it or not. He will literally send everyone in the class a chart of the best and worst teams. Some many things to do every weeks, tests, questions, group project, business simulation, etc.

4 graded group works per week plus one graded quiz evaluating the content of the course that will be studied the next day... Prof. struggles managing student participation and the class pace is very slow. Messy slides and elements constantly overlap. Prof. doesn't always know answers to his own examples and writes bad answers without checking them.
